title: Ep 394: Get Ready For A 30% Pullback
itunes:title: Get Ready For A 30% Pullback
description:
Rich Suttmeier,  CEO & Founder of Global Market Consultants, sees a 30% correction in the S&P 500.   He predicts higher interest rates and another possible housing collapse before year-end. 
Rich suggests taking profits in oil stocks following the huge surge in the sector.  He also sees a major pullback in mining stocks over the next few months.
